// TODO Add a couple lines about each project
const data = [
  {
    title: "Electronic Health Records",
    subtitle: "2015 BVP Hackathon",
    image:
      "https://www.google.com/imgres?imgurl=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.researchgate.net%2Fpublication%2F331069965%2Ffigure%2Ffig1%2FAS%3A725838542680075%401550064802730%2FUS-pilot-project-Blockchain-for-Hospitals.png&imgrefurl=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.researchgate.net%2Ffigure%2FUS-pilot-project-Blockchain-for-Hospitals_fig1_331069965&tbnid=mR3tDvOCDvCIYM&vet=12ahUKEwjw4ObOkKTyAhUZi0sFHeLsAAQQMygGegUIARC4AQ..i&docid=1NgONOVfTZNzIM&w=850&h=633&q=high%20quality%20image%20EHR%20on%20blockchain&ved=2ahUKEwjw4ObOkKTyAhUZi0sFHeLsAAQQMygGegUIARC4AQ",
    date: "2021-04-20",
    desc:
      "Built for a social impact hackathon. " +
      "NearestDollar connected to your bank accounts, credit cards, " +
      "or debit cards and rounded up your purchases to donate the balance to " +
      "the charity of your choice.",
  },
  {
    title: "Harvest",
    subtitle: "Won 3rd. place in 2015 Techcrunch Disrupt SF Hackathon",
    link: "https://devpost.com/software/harvest",
    image: "/images/projects/harvest.jpg",
    date: "2015-09-20",
    desc:
      "Won ~ $7000 in prizes for an advanced, low cost monitoring solution " +
      "for crops. Harvest was designed to catch irrigation leaks, overwatering, " +
      "and nutrient deficiencies at an affordable price for the developing world.",
  },
  {
    title: "Space Potato",
    subtitle: "A kickstarter funded potato powered weather balloon.",
    link: "http://www.spacepotato.org",
    image: "/images/projects/spacepotato.jpg",
    date: "2015-06-28",
    desc:
      "Launched a potato battery powered weather balloon with two cameras " +
      "and gps transponder. Resulting photos were published in a coffee table book. " +
      "You can email me for a copy.",
  },
  {
    title: "Cat Detector",
    subtitle: "A convolutional neural network to classify cats! (and dogs)",
    image: "/images/projects/catdetector.jpg",
    date: "2015-05-15",
    desc:
      "Trained a convolutional neural network to classify between ~ 80 cats breeds. " +
      "Over 60,000 cats were classified before server bills made the project too expensive " +
      "to continue hosting.",
  },
];

export default data;
